&lt;p&gt;The Endoscopy Unit at Hinchingbrook Hospital is looking to expand its services in order to meet the ever growing demand for endoscopic procedures. We offer a work environment with state of the art facilities and a real commitment to your career.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are currently recruiting Nurses either with or without Endoscopy experience, to join our dedicated team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting, fast paced and challenging Unit to work on. You need to have a passion for delivering high standards of care, commitment to sharing your knowledge and skills and enthusiasm to help drive our services forward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidates will be fully supported with personalized development plans to assist in reaching your full potential and career goals. Along with an induction programme which will include supernumerary periods, preceptorship and close support from a named mentor and clinical educator.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are a confident and highly motivated individual who is keen to develop your skills through practice and further education and training, and are excited about becoming a member of the Endoscopy Team, then please get in touch.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for 2 full time and 1 part time fixed term contracts&lt;/p&gt;
